#: ../../../CONTRIBUTING.rst:3
msgid "Contributing"
msgstr "Contribuer"

#: ../../../CONTRIBUTING.rst:5
msgid ""
"Contributions are welcome, and they are greatly appreciated! Every little "
"bit helps, and credit will always be given. Have a look at the `great guide "
"<https://docs.sunpy.org/en/latest/dev_guide/contents/newcomers.html>`_ from "
"the `sunpy project <https://sunpy.org>`_ which provides advice for new "
"contributors."
msgstr ""
"Les contributions sont les bienvenues et très appréciées ! Chaque petite "
"contribution compte, et les crédits seront toujours accordés. Consultez le "
"`excellent guide "
"<https://docs.sunpy.org/en/latest/dev_guide/contents/newcomers.html>`_ du "
"`projet sunpy <https://sunpy.org>`_ qui fournit des conseils aux nouveaux "
"contributeurs."

#: ../../../CONTRIBUTING.rst:9
msgid ""
"All contributors will be treated with respect and everyone is expected to "
"comply with the SunPy `Code of Conduct <https://sunpy.org/coc>`_."
msgstr ""
"Tous les contributeurs seront traités avec respect et chacun est tenu de "
"respecter le `Code de conduite <https://sunpy.org/coc>`_ de SunPy."
